Package: lintrsecurity
Title: Security-Focused Linters for R Code
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tyler", "Smith", , "tylerjssmith@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides linters for use with the 'lintr' package to detect
    security-relevant patterns in R source code. Targeted patterns include
    dangerous constructs in package lifecycle hooks, calls to system execution
    functions, and network calls that may exfiltrate data or fetch malicious
    payloads. Intended to support secure R package development and supply
    chain security research.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/tylerjssmith/lintrsecurity
BugReports: https://github.com/tylerjssmith/lintrsecurity/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 8.0.0
